Package FestivalPlanner.TileMap

Contains classes responsible for handling the graphical representation/simulation of our software in the form of TileMaps.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Layer
    Represents one Layer in TileMap.
    ObjectLayer
    Represents one ObjectLayer in TileMap
    Tile
    Contains attributes and methods for an individual tile.
    TileLayer
    Contains attributes and methods for one Layer with tiles in TileMap.
    TileManager
    Contains methods to store one instance of each tile to prevent duplicates.
    TileMap
    Contains information of a TileMap.
    TileObject
    Represents an object stored in a .JSON file.

Package FestivalPlanner.TileMap Description

Contains classes responsible for handling the graphical representation/simulation of our software in the form of TileMaps.
